《'''Flappy Bird'''》（飞扬的小鸟）是一款2013年[[鳥飛|鳥飛類]]遊戲，由[[越南|越南]][[河內|河內]]獨立遊戲开发者[[阮河東|阮河東]]（Dong Nguyen）開發<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cn.vietnamplus.vn/Home/%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8FFlappy-bird%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1/20142/32736.vnplus |title=火爆全球的越南游戏Flappy bird作者讲述下架理由 |accessdate=2014-02-26 |archive-date=2014-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229212516/http://cn.vietnamplus.vn/Home/%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8FFlappy-bird%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%AE%B2%E8%BF%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1/20142/32736.vnplus |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/news/68468.html “胖鸟”是如何冲天的——Flappy Bird的连锁反应] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apdnews.com/news/68468.html |date=20140221233756 }}，亚太日报，2014年2月14日</ref><ref name="thanhnien">{{vi}} {{cite news|url=http://www.thanhnien.com.vn/pages/20140206/chang-trai-viet-game-flappy-bird-gay-sot-toan-cau.aspx|title=Chàng trai viết game Flappy Bird gây sốt toàn cầu|author=Đan Hạ|publisher=Thanh Nien|date=2014-02-06|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106091721/http://www.thanhnien.com.vn/pages/20140206/chang-trai-viet-game-flappy-bird-gay-sot-toan-cau.aspx|archive-date=2014-11-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="telegraph">{{cite web|last=Williams|first=Rhiannon|title=What is Flappy Bird? The game taking the App Store by storm|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/10604366/What-is-Flappy-Bird-The-game-taking-the-App-Store-by-storm.html|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=30 January 2014|archive-date=2016-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202014822/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/10604366/What-is-Flappy-Bird-The-game-taking-the-App-Store-by-storm.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另一個獨立遊戲开发商.GEARS Studios發佈。<ref name="philly"/>此遊戲原本於2013年5月發佈，平台為[[iPhone_5|iPhone 5]]。同年9月，作者將遊戲更新至[[iOS_6|iOS 6]]。<ref name="sentralgamer">{{cite web |author=Published on January 21st, 2014 by Jamie84303 |url=http://www.sentralgamer.com/flappy-bird-ios/ |title=Flappy Bird [iOS |publisher=SentralGamer |date=2014-01-21 |accessdate=2014-01-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140131142144/http://www.sentralgamer.com/flappy-bird-ios/ |archivedate=2014-01-31 }}</ref>於2014年1月，此遊戲成為美國及中國iTunes最受歡迎免費應用軟件<ref name="sentralgamer"/>，並在同月被英國App Store描述為「新[[憤怒鳥|憤怒鳥]]」。<ref name="telegraph"/>此遊戲更成為1月下載次數最多的免費應用軟件。<ref name="stokesentinel">{{cite web |last=Sentinel |first=The |url=http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/frustrated-Stokies-blast-Flappy-Bird-game-Twitter/story-20538032-detail/story.html |title=As frustrated Stokies blast Flappy Bird game on Twitter we ask: What's your favourite smartphone app? |publisher=Stoke Sentinel |date= |accessdate=2014-01-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222012742/http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/frustrated-Stokies-blast-Flappy-Bird-game-Twitter/story-20538032-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-02-22 }}</ref>此遊戲的下載次數至今已超過5000萬次。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-26090330|title=Flappy Bird Windows Phone version appears on website|author=Matthew Wall|publisher=BBC|date=2014-02-07|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2014-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208222043/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-26090330|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==玩法==
[[檔案:Flappy_Bird_Screenshot.png|thumb]]
游戏的玩法为：操控小鳥飛行且避開綠色的管道；如果小鳥碰到了障礙物，遊戲就會結束。每當小鳥飛過一組管道，玩家就會獲得一分。<ref>{{cite web|last=Haynes|first=Danielle|title=Flappy Birds dominates app lists|url=http://www.upi.com/blog/2014/01/26/Flappy-Birds-dominates-app-lists/8271390760147/|publisher=UPI|accessdate=30 January 2014|archive-date=2014-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140130130947/http://www.upi.com/blog/2014/01/26/Flappy-Birds-dominates-app-lists/8271390760147|dead-url=no}}</ref>此遊戲以難度著稱，大部份玩家均僅獲得個位數的分數。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.droidreport.com/flappy-bird-high-score-leads-chicago-murder-5503|title=Flappy Bird High Score Leads To Chicago Murder?|publisher=Droid Report|author=Dmitry Sheynin|accessdate=2014-02-09|date=2014-02-03|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222231439/http://www.droidreport.com/flappy-bird-high-score-leads-chicago-murder-5503|dead-url=no}}</ref>此遊戲的畫質類似於《[[超級瑪利歐兄弟|超級瑪利歐兄弟]]》，其遊戲機制非常基本，且內置[[廣告|廣告]]。<ref name="ibt">{{cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/frustrating-flappy-bird-tops-app-list-what-are-toughest-games-ever-made-1434184 |title=Frustrating Flappy Bird Tops App List: What Are the Toughest Games Ever Made? |publisher=Ibtimes.co.uk |date=2012-05-11 |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131202446/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/frustrating-flappy-bird-tops-app-list-what-are-toughest-games-ever-made-1434184 |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據科技新聞及媒體網絡[[The_Verge|The Verge]]的報告，此遊戲於2014年初每天為作者帶來50,000美金的廣告收益。<ref name="Verge1">{{cite web|author=Ellis Hamburger|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/5/5383708/flappy-bird-revenue-50-k-per-day-dong-nguyen-interview|title=Indie smash hit 'Flappy Bird' racks up $50K per day in ad revenue|publisher=The Verge|date=2014-02-05|accessdate=2014-02-06|archive-date=2017-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128073903/http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/5/5383708/flappy-bird-revenue-50-k-per-day-dong-nguyen-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==製作==
《Flappy Bird》是由阮河东開發。起初，Flappy Bird這一角色是於2012年為一個[[平台遊戲|平台遊戲]]而創，但阮哈東後來取消開發該平台遊戲。之後，他用了2至3天開發《Flappy Bird》，並重新使用Flappy Bird這一角色。阮河東指出，他開發此遊戲時並沒有為難玩家的意圖。<ref>{{cite news|last=Heney|first=Elaine|title=How to make Flappy Bird, #1 app – Interview with game developer Dong Nguyen: Updated|url=http://www.thechocolatelabapps.com/how-to-make-flappy-bird/|newspaper=Chocolate Lab Apps|date=31 January 2014|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2014-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140206211056/http://www.thechocolatelabapps.com/how-to-make-flappy-bird/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==下架==
於2014年2月9日，阮河東在[[twitter|twitter]]上發言，指出他計劃將遊戲下架。他說：「《Flappy Bird》用戶們，我很抱歉，在22小時後，我會將《Flappy Bird》下架。我再也無法忍受了。」<ref name="cannottakethisanymore">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/dongatory/status/432227971173068800 |title=Twitter / dongatory: I am sorry 'Flappy Bird' users |publisher=Twitter.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-09 |archive-date=2014-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209025416/https://twitter.com/dongatory/status/432227971173068800 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ait/201402090261-1.aspx Flappy Bird將下架 原因未明] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ait/201402090261-1.aspx |date=20140221233615 }}，中央社，2014年2月9日</ref>他亦指出下架決定「與法律問題無關」。<ref name="nothingtodowithlegalissues">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/dongatory/status/432228383095668737 |title=Twitter / dongatory: It is not anything related |publisher=Twitter.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-09 |archive-date=2014-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208205047/https://twitter.com/dongatory/status/432228383095668737 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==評價==
《Flappy Bird》獲《[[赫芬頓郵報|赫芬頓郵報]]》批評，指出此遊戲是一個「瘋狂地惱人、困難和令人沮喪的遊戲」，且「結合了超陡峭的難度曲線、差劣無聊的畫質和生硬的動作」。<ref name="huffingtonpost">{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/01/29/flappy-bird-tips_n_4686221.html |title=Flappy Bird Tips: How To Get A High Score Without Cheats |publisher=Huffingtonpost.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131094648/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/01/29/flappy-bird-tips_n_4686221.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是，Amongtech.com的珍妮弗·懷特塞德卻給予一個更正面的評價。她指出此遊戲可能因其令人上癮的遊戲模式、Candy Crush的受歡迎程度下降和炒作而超越《[[Candy_Crush_Saga|Candy Crush Saga]]》成為2014年最受歡迎遊戲。<ref name="amongtech">{{cite web |last=Whiteside |first=Jenifer |url=http://www.amongtech.com/could-flappy-bird-beat-candy-crush-as-the-most-popular-mobile-game-of-2014/ |title=Could Flappy Bird beat Candy Crush as the most popular Game of 2014? |publisher=Amongtech.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201122902/http://www.amongtech.com/could-flappy-bird-beat-candy-crush-as-the-most-popular-mobile-game-of-2014/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此遊戲的難度亦導致不少玩家感到憤怒，其中一位玩家更指出他自己用了半小時才能獲得5分。<ref name="philly">{{cite web |author=Mike Bertha, Philly.com |url=http://www.philly.com/philly/blogs/trending/Flappy-Bird-app-game-iPhone-Android-obsessed-cheats-impossible-Ironpants.html |title=Everything you need to know about your new favorite cell phone game, 'Flappy Bird' |publisher=Philly.com |date=2012-10-22 |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131090256/http://www.philly.com/philly/blogs/trending/Flappy-Bird-app-game-iPhone-Android-obsessed-cheats-impossible-Ironpants.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據作者本人指出<ref name="twitter">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/dongatory/status/428363898920529920 |title=Twitter / dongatory: @dmatttx Yes, it is easier on Android |publisher=Twitter.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227140245/https://twitter.com/dongatory/status/428363898920529920 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此遊戲的[[Android|Android]]版本要比[[iOS|iOS]]版本容易。<ref name="phonesreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.phonesreview.co.uk/2014/01/30/flappy-bird-android-app-easier-than-ios/ |title=Flappy Bird Android app easier than iOS » Phone Reviews |publisher=Phonesreview.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-01-31 |archive-date=2014-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131095809/http://www.phonesreview.co.uk/2014/01/30/flappy-bird-android-app-easier-than-ios/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外，此遊戲亦被稱為「App Store的毒品」（{{lang|en|Drug of the App Store}}）。<ref name="philly"/>

==爭議==
因為此遊戲的迅速爆紅，所以部份媒體質疑作者在2014年初利用機器人大幅增加此遊戲的下載次數。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bluecloudsolutions.com/blog/flappy-birds-smoke-mirrors-scamming-app-store/ |title=Flappy Bird's Smoke & Mirrors - Is Something Fishy Going On? |publisher=Bluecloudsolutions.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-05 |archive-date=2014-02-05 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140205133342/http://www.bluecloudsolutions.com/blog/flappy-birds-smoke-mirrors-scamming-app-store/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>當阮河東被《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》採訪時，他說：「我尊重所有其他人的意見。我不會因提出任何評論。我希望我的遊戲能得到和平。」<ref>{{cite news|last=Williams|first=Rhiannon|title=Flappy Bird: 'too good to be true?'|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/10615036/Flappy-Bird-too-good-to-be-true.html|accessdate=5 February 2014|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=4 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209062245/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/10615036/Flappy-Bird-too-good-to-be-true.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，當《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》提出相同的問題時，阮河東卻在twitter上說：「這並不要緊。難道你不這樣覺得嗎？……如果我真的偽造了下載次數，蘋果公司應該還會讓它存活多幾個月。」 <ref name="Newsweek">{{cite web|url=http://www.newsweek.com/flappy-bird-cooking-its-itunes-rank-228016|title=Is Flappy Bird Cooking its iTunes Rank?|publisher=Newsweek|author=Kloc, Joe|date=2014-02-04|accessdate=2014-02-04|archive-date=2014-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205070647/http://www.newsweek.com/flappy-bird-cooking-its-itunes-rank-228016|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此遊戲亦被[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]批評公開使用超級瑪利歐的設計樣式，並將遊戲等同於「盗窃」。<ref name="kotaku">{{cite web |author=2/06/14 12:35pm Yesterday 12:35pm |url=http://kotaku.com/flappy-bird-is-making-50-000-a-day-off-ripped-art-1517498140 |title=Flappy Bird Is Making $50,000 A Day Off Ripped Art |publisher=Kotaku.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archive-date=2014-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209064602/http://kotaku.com/flappy-bird-is-making-50-000-a-day-off-ripped-art-1517498140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此遊戲在上市後有大量的衍生作品出現，例如Hacker Diary<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://googledrive.com/host/0B1UwfXyBN6kfVHFiNUcyUkcwYWs/ |title=Hacker Diary |accessdate=2014-02-18 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222100651/https://googledrive.com/host/0B1UwfXyBN6kfVHFiNUcyUkcwYWs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、Flappy MMO、Flappy fario 等作品出現，Google 和 Apple 甚至將全部含有Flappy 名稱的遊戲都一起下架，避免形成Flappy zoo的情況出現。

== 影响 ==
Google在其手机操作系统[[Android歷史版本#Android_5.0_Lollipop|Android 5.0]]及Android 6.0中，加入了与Flappy Bird很相似的系统彩蛋，可以通过点击屏幕控制一个Android机器人通过各种由棒棒糖组成的障碍。<ref>[http://www.theverge.com/2014/10/17/6995051/android-5-0-lollipop-flappy-droid-easter-egg Android 5.0 Lollipop's Easter egg is a Flappy Bird clone] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/10/17/6995051/android-5-0-lollipop-flappy-droid-easter-egg |date=20141220140116 }}.TheVerge.October 17, 2014.[December 22, 2014].</ref>

